"pid":"df7973530dfaf2fbfbdc9ecd9d4b7311433fa706","tid":2174270,"uid":11521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T06:55:27.000Z","msg":"咁多位都好神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3e497e3442195e90b9e50369a3f371a243eb93d","tid":2174270,"uid":44935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T07:46:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8b92325960ca7db4b0118a560c8bfdbd73912ae","tid":2174270,"uid":178205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T07:51:14.000Z","msg":"有冇3成人用到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲要唔平"},{"pid":"b37071a577815d385b3c2c86bfc1188b13a33e89","tid":2174270,"uid":10890,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b3e497e3442195e90b9e50369a3f371a243eb93d","tid":2174270,"uid":44935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T07:46:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T07:53:13.000Z","msg":"腫瘤係一大堆cancer cells<br />\nT-cell去到現場就要一層層咁殺入去<br />\n<br />\n即係好似消防打火咁<br />\n要喺個火最外圍開始打<br />\n<br />\nT cell打到咁上下就會死<br />\n但同一時間cancer cell又會不斷分裂<br />\n所以就會變咗如果T cell去唔切個tumour度<br />\n或者殺得唔夠快<br />\n就會被cancer cell反cup"},{"pid":"8ce0e408f325d96ad340e8c1ca24369efd4c0fe6","tid":2174270,"uid":38861,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b3e497e3442195e90b9e50369a3f371a243eb93d","tid":2174270,"uid":44935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T07:46:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T07:53:37.000Z","msg":"點樣確保T cell可以有效殺入癌細胞內部，喺應用上仲係處於好初步階段。<br />\n<br />\n依我所知暫時較為領前的藥係針對STING pathway，但處於有一系列問題需要解決的階段。"},{"pid":"edafefe